Cell["\<\
to get an image of a Tiger. Then apply EdgeDetect, and then ColorNegate. Look \
up the function ImageCompose to compose the original image with the \
EdgeDetected and ColorNegated version.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.81020761824253*^9, 
