  3.645511574315887*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f2628e21-66e3-4d7f-95e6-\
1c00ea99c79c"],

Cell["\<\
If you want the output from a variable to be different every time it is used, \
you must use SetDelayed (:=).\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.6455115809969063`*^9, 
  3.64551159937128*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0a8a1e66-b642-414c-916b-\
1ac7b7d29ddb"],

