  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " 10,  ",
 StyleBox[ButtonBox["Association",
  BaseStyle->"Link",
  ButtonData->"paclet:ref/Association"],
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " was added to ",
 StyleBox["Mathematica",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " to allow for full associative arrays. An association can be defined as \
follows."
}], "Text",
